{"id":132,"date":"2019-08-03T23:07:14","date_gmt":"2019-08-03T16:07:14","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/kientruc2.ninhbinhweb.info\/?p=132"},"modified":"2019-08-04T16:28:55","modified_gmt":"2019-08-04T09:28:55","slug":"thiet-ke-quan-ca-phe","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"http:\/\/kientruc2.ninhbinhweb.info\/thiet-ke-quan-ca-phe\/","title":{"rendered":"Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf qu\u00e1n c\u00e0 ph\u00ea"},"content":{"rendered":"<h2><strong>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf qu\u00e1n cafe<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p>Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ebfn qu\u00e1n cafe ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c ly cafe v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u00f3i quen c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi vi\u1ec7t. Qu\u00e1n cafe l\u00e0 n\u01a1i c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n tr\u1ebb g\u1eb7p nhau \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n, h\u1eb9n h\u00f2.\u00a0Ch\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y m\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh kinh doanh qu\u00e1n cafe ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n.\u00a0Ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u qu\u00e1n cafe n\u00ean lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh kinh doanh n\u00e0y c\u00f3 t\u00ednh c\u1ea1nh tranh cao. Qu\u00e1n cafe c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i thu h\u00fat th\u1eadt nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch m\u1edbi c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i nhu\u1eadn. M\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c qu\u00e1n \u0111\u00f4ng hay nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n qu\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o kh\u00f4ng gian c\u1ee7a qu\u00e1n. N\u00f3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb9p, c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o, sang tr\u1ecdng hay kh\u00f4ng.<\/p>\n<p>B\u1ee1i th\u1ebf ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ee7 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t qu\u00e1n cafe \u0111\u1ed9c l\u1ea1, c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n, phong c\u00e1ch ri\u00eang.\u00a0\u00a0C\u00f2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1ch th\u00ec mong mu\u1ed1n th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c ly cafe trong kh\u00f4ng gian sang tr\u1ecdng, \u0111\u1ecdc \u0111\u00e1o. Cho n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf qu\u00e1n cafe r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c bu\u00f4n b\u00e1n c\u1ee7a qu\u00e1n.<\/p>\n<p>Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t qu\u00e1n cafe \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho kh\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5. N\u00ean b\u1ea1n h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 cho c\u00f4ng ty XD \u0110\u1ea1i Thanh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 b\u1ea1n thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf m\u1ed9t qu\u00e1n cafe \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00e3 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf h\u00e0ng tr\u0103m qu\u00e1n cafe mang \u0111\u1eadm d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n v\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch ri\u00eang.<\/p>\n<h3><strong>KHI S\u1eec D\u1ee4NG D\u1ecaCH V\u1ee4 C\u1ee6A CH\u00daNG T\u00d4I QU\u00dd KH\u00c1CH H\u00c0NG S\u1ebc \u0110\u01af\u1ee2C G\u00cc?<\/strong><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>C\u00f4ng ty ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n, nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh. S\u1ebd t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n v\u00e0\u00a0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p c\u00e1c th\u1eafc m\u1eafc c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh ch\u00f3ng.<\/li>\n<li>Ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m t\u1ed1i \u0111a chi ph\u00ed: Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf khoa h\u1ecdc nh\u1ea5t. \u0110\u01b0a ra ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u1eadt t\u01b0. V\u00e0 t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/li>\n<li>T\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng kh\u00f4ng gian: Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n thi c\u00f4ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c di\u1ec7n t\u00edch l\u00e0m cho qu\u00e1n cafe r\u1ed1ng r\u00e3i h\u01a1n. S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1ef1 h\u00e0i h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c m\u00e0u s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m cho b\u1ea1n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u00f5ng r\u00e3i tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i. T\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng gian \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tho\u00e1n m\u00e1t<\/li>\n<li>Ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m th\u1eddi gian: Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong lich v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\u00a0 N\u00ean s\u1ebd t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n nhanh nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh l\u00e3ng ph\u00ed th\u1eddi gian. T\u01b0 v\u1ea5n l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn v\u1eadt t\u01b0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh ch\u00f3ng. \u0110\u01b0a ra ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ed1i \u01b0u nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh \u0111\u00fang ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u00fat ng\u1eafn th\u1eddi gian n\u1ebfu kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f2n c\u00f3 quy tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c khoa h\u1ecdc tr\u00e1nh l\u00e3ng ph\u00ed th\u1eddi gian c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><strong>QUY TR\u00ccNH THI\u1ebeT K\u1ebe:<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>B\u01b0\u1edbc 1: Khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u th\u1eeb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd g\u1ecdi t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n s\u01a1 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng hi\u1ec3u. N\u1ebfu kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd th\u00ec ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh g\u1eb7p kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n s\u00e2u h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<p>B\u01b0\u1edbc 2: \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. Th\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd cho nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1ea3o s\u00e1t, l\u00ean ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf. Khi l\u00ean ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n th\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n kh\u00e1c nhau. \u0110\u1ec3 tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. N\u1ebfu kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf th\u00ec ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng.<\/p>\n<p>B\u01b0\u1edbc 3: Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u0169ng c\u1ea5p th\u00f4ng tin, \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi phong th\u1ee7y c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0.<\/p>\n<p>B\u01b0\u1edbc 4: Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u00e0 chi ph\u00ed thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf th\u00ec ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf.<\/p>\n<p>B\u01b0\u1edbc 5: Sau khi \u0111\u00e3 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf xong th\u00ec b\u00e0n giao b\u1ea3n v\u1ebd cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n<h3><strong>M\u1ed8T S\u1ed0 M\u1eaaU QU\u00c1N CAFE \u0110\u1eb8P<\/strong><\/h3>\n<h4><strong>M\u1eabu qu\u00e1n cafe s\u00e2n v\u01b0\u1eddn.<\/strong><\/h4>\n<p>Qu\u00e1n c\u00e0 ph\u00ea ng\u1eadp tr\u00e0n c\u00e2y xanh, n\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u00e1 l\u00e0 n\u01a1i l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang ta th\u01b0 gi\u1ea3n sau 1 ng\u00e0y l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u0103n th\u1eb3ng. H\u1ea7u h\u1ebft t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c qu\u00e1n cafe s\u00e2n v\u01b0\u1eddn \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng gian y\u00ean t\u0129nh.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2515\" src=\"https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/thiet-ke-cafe-san-vuon.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 839px) 100vw, 839px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/thiet-ke-cafe-san-vuon.png 839w, https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/thiet-ke-cafe-san-vuon-300x246.png 300w, https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/thiet-ke-cafe-san-vuon-768x630.png 768w\" alt=\"\" width=\"839\" height=\"688\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf qu\u00e1n cafe s\u00e2n v\u01b0\u1eddn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a c\u1ee9 \u0111em c\u00e2y xanh v\u00e0o b\u1ecf \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. M\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i theo m\u00f4t b\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c, b\u1ed1 tr\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, khoa h\u1ecdc. Qu\u00e1n cafe c\u00f3 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf c\u00e2y xanh t\u1ea1o kh\u00f4ng gian m\u00e1t m\u1ebd, g\u1ea7n g\u1eedi v\u1edbi thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2516 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/cafe_san_vuon_dien_tich_lon_datsaigoncafe04.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/cafe_san_vuon_dien_tich_lon_datsaigoncafe04.jpg 750w, https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/cafe_san_vuon_dien_tich_lon_datsaigoncafe04-300x160.jpg 300w\" alt=\"\" width=\"750\" height=\"400\" \/><\/p>\n<p>M\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf qu\u00e1n cafe s\u00e2n v\u01b0\u1eddn. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean. \u0110\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed \u1ea5m c\u00fang v\u00e0 trong l\u00e0nh.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2519 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/thiet-ke-noi-that-quan-cafe-san-vuon2.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 666px) 100vw, 666px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/thiet-ke-noi-that-quan-cafe-san-vuon2.jpg 666w, https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/thiet-ke-noi-that-quan-cafe-san-vuon2-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/thiet-ke-noi-that-quan-cafe-san-vuon2-320x240.jpg 320w\" alt=\"\" width=\"666\" height=\"500\" \/><\/p>\n<p>M\u1eabu qu\u00e1n cafe n\u00e0y n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e0u s\u1eafc tao nh\u00e3, nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0n. \u0110\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng gian th\u01b0 gi\u1ea3n tho\u00e1i m\u00e1i.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2520 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/dai-dien-thiet-ke-quan-cf-san-vuon-dep-o-tra-vinh-500x320.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/dai-dien-thiet-ke-quan-cf-san-vuon-dep-o-tra-vinh-500x320.jpg 500w, https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/dai-dien-thiet-ke-quan-cf-san-vuon-dep-o-tra-vinh-500x320-300x192.jpg 300w\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"320\" \/><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h4><strong>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf qu\u00e1n cafe h\u1ed3 c\u00e1 koi<\/strong><\/h4>\n<p>Qu\u00e1n cafe h\u1ed3 c\u00e1 koi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh qu\u00e1n cafe m\u1edbi m\u1ebd. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00edch th\u00fa, l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u1edbi cho c\u00e1c ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2522 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/ho-ca-koi-cafe.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/ho-ca-koi-cafe.jpg 640w, https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/ho-ca-koi-cafe-300x183.jpg 300w\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"390\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Qu\u00e1n cafe h\u1ed3 c\u00e1 koi l\u00e0n\u01a1i l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u01b0 gi\u1ea3n, ng\u00e1m nh\u00ecn c\u1ea3nh quan. \u0110i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi h\u1ed3 c\u00e1 koi l\u00e0 c\u00e2y xanh v\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc. T\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t b\u00e0u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed trong l\u00e0nh g\u1ea7n g\u1ee7i v\u1edbi thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2523\" src=\"https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/5b080b6879460-1.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/5b080b6879460-1.jpg 960w, https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/5b080b6879460-1-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/5b080b6879460-1-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/5b080b6879460-1-320x240.jpg 320w\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"720\" \/><\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf m\u1edbi m\u1ebd, \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o. Thu h\u00fat \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2524 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/photo-1-15334327240121689400708.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/photo-1-15334327240121689400708.jpg 800w, https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/photo-1-15334327240121689400708-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/photo-1-15334327240121689400708-768x512.jpg 768w\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" \/><\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1eabu qu\u00e1n cafe t\u00e2n d\u1ee5ng \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng trong m\u00e1t. Tr\u00ean c\u00f3 c\u00e2y xanh d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u00f3 c\u00e1 \u0111\u00e2y qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c l\u00e0 m\u1eabu qu\u00e1n cafe l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u01b0 gi\u1ea3n sau nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2525 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/Nia-Cafe.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/Nia-Cafe.jpg 660w, https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/Nia-Cafe-300x200.jpg 300w\" alt=\"\" width=\"660\" height=\"440\" \/><\/p>\n<h4><strong>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf qu\u00e1n cafe theo phong c\u00e1ch H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c<\/strong><\/h4>\n<p>Hi\u00ean nay th\u00ec phong c\u00e1ch h\u00e0n qu\u1ed1c \u0111ang \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n tr\u1ebb Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Nh\u1eefng qu\u00e1n cafe theo phong c\u00e1ch H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n tr\u1ebb\u00a0 y\u00eau th\u00edch.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2526 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/thiet-ke-quan-cafe-theo-phong-cach-han-quoc-cafe-takeaway2.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/thiet-ke-quan-cafe-theo-phong-cach-han-quoc-cafe-takeaway2.jpg 500w, https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/thiet-ke-quan-cafe-theo-phong-cach-han-quoc-cafe-takeaway2-300x200.jpg 300w\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c qu\u00e1n cafe H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n tr\u1ebb. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady m\u00e0\u00a0 kh\u00f4ng gian qu\u00e1n cafe n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9ng, tr\u1ebb trung, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 y\u00ean l\u1eb7ng nh\u01b0 cafe s\u00e2n v\u01b0\u1eddn.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2527 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/thiet-ke-quan-cafe-han-quoc-1.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/thiet-ke-quan-cafe-han-quoc-1.jpg 600w, https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/thiet-ke-quan-cafe-han-quoc-1-300x200.jpg 300w\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" \/><\/p>\n<p>T\u00f4ng m\u00e0u ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a qu\u00e1n l\u00e0 m\u00e0u n\u00e2u. T\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, \u1ea5m c\u00fang v\u00e0 s\u1ea1ch s\u1ebd. K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e2y xanh t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 g\u1ea7n g\u1ee7i. N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng l\u00e0 g\u1ed7 t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 m\u1edbi m\u1ebb.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2528 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/bi-quyet-trang-tri-quan-cafe.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/bi-quyet-trang-tri-quan-cafe.jpg 600w, https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/bi-quyet-trang-tri-quan-cafe-300x221.jpg 300w\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"441\" \/><\/p>\n<h4><strong>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf qu\u00e1n cafe theo phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n.<\/strong><\/h4>\n<p>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu qu\u00e1n cafe hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i th\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn th\u00edch kh\u00f4ng gian c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n. C\u00f3 ch\u00fat c\u1ed5 x\u01b0a \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4n v\u1edbi nhau \u00f4n l\u1ea1i k\u1ef9 ni\u1ec7m ng\u00e0y x\u01b0a.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2530\" src=\"https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/thiet-ke-cua-hang-theo-phong-cach-vintage-13.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/thiet-ke-cua-hang-theo-phong-cach-vintage-13.jpg 1000w, https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/thiet-ke-cua-hang-theo-phong-cach-vintage-13-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/thiet-ke-cua-hang-theo-phong-cach-vintage-13-768x513.jpg 768w\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"668\" \/><\/p>\n<p>M\u00e0u s\u1eafc quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. M\u00e0u s\u1eafc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 m\u00e0u c\u00f3 t\u00ednh n\u00f3ng, \u1ea5m \u00e1m. N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nguy\u00ean v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean nh\u01b0 tre, g\u1ed7, m\u00e2y.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2532 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/noi-that-nha-hang-Nhat2.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/noi-that-nha-hang-Nhat2.jpg 560w, https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/noi-that-nha-hang-Nhat2-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/xaydungdaithanh.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/noi-that-nha-hang-Nhat2-320x240.jpg 320w\" alt=\"\" width=\"560\" height=\"420\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong m\u1eabu qu\u00e1n cafe n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng nh\u00e2n t\u1ea1o. Th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00e1c h\u1ecda ti\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng l\u00e0 c\u1ed5 x\u01b0<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf qu\u00e1n cafe Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ebfn qu\u00e1n cafe ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c ly cafe v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u00f3i quen c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi vi\u1ec7t. Qu\u00e1n cafe l\u00e0 n\u01a1i c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n tr\u1ebb g\u1eb7p nhau \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n, h\u1eb9n h\u00f2.\u00a0Ch\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y m\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh kinh doanh qu\u00e1n cafe ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n.\u00a0Ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng &#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":133,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[2],"tags":[9,8],"yst_prominent_words":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/kientruc2.ninhbinhweb.info\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/132"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/kientruc2.ninhbinhweb.info\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/kientruc2.ninhbinhweb.info\/wp-json\/wp\/